---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout 
    title="Agencia de Marketing Digital | SEMTIC" 
    description="Estrategias de marketing digital efectivas para potenciar tu marca, atraer clientes e incrementar tus ventas online."
    image="https://semtic.cl/og-servicios.png">

    <!-- SECCIÓN 1: HERO -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center pt-32 pb-20 overflow-hidden" style="z-index: 10;">
        <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-64 md:w-96 h-64 md:h-96 bg-[#00f2ea] rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[128px] opacity-20 animate-pulse"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-64 md:w-96 h-64 md:h-96 bg-[#4f46e5] rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[128px] opacity-20 animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
                Agencia de Marketing Digital <br class="hidden lg:block"/><span class="text-gradient">que consigue Clientes Reales para tu Negocio.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10 font-light leading-relaxed">
                Deja de gastar dinero en "likes" y empieza a invertir en conversiones. Diseñamos estrategias a medida para empresas en Limache, Viña del Mar, Marga Marga y todo Chile.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECCIÓN 2: EL "DOLOR" DEL CLIENTE -->
    <section class="py-10 md:py-20 relative" style="z-index: 10;">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto p-10 md:p-16 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-[#0a0a1a]/80 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl text-center relative overflow-hidden shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)]">
                <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-3/4 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#4f46e5] to-transparent opacity-50"></div>
                <h2 class="text-sm md:text-base font-bold mb-6 text-[#4f46e5] tracking-[0.25em] uppercase">¿Frustrado con tus Redes Sociales?</h2>
                <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed font-light">
                    ¿Sientes que publicas en redes sociales pero <span class="text-[#4f46e5] font-medium">tu teléfono no suena?</span> La mayoría de las agencias se enfocan en métricas de vanidad que no pagan las cuentas. En Semtic, nuestro único objetivo es que tu inversión retorne en forma de prospectos calificados y ventas reales.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECCIÓN 3: NUESTRA SOLUCIÓN (Metodología) -->
    <section class="py-20 relative" style="z-index: 10; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.3), rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.6));">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-10">
                <!-- Tarjeta 1 - Estrategias Basadas en Datos -->
                <div class="group relative p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl bg-[#0a0a1a]/50 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-md hover:border-[#4f46e5]/40 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-xl hover:shadow-[0_10px_40px_-15px_rgba(79,70,229,0.3)]">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4f46e5]/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 rounded-3xl transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 mb-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4f46e5]/20 to-transparent flex items-center justify-center text-[#4f46e5] border border-[#4f46e5]/20 group-hover:bg-[#4f46e5]/30 transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8 drop-shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(79,70,229,0.5)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] leading-tight">Estrategias Basadas en Datos</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            Analizamos tu mercado y atacamos donde está tu cliente ideal.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Tarjeta 2 - Embudos de Venta (Funnels) -->
                <div class="group relative p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl bg-[#0a0a1a]/50 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-md hover:border-[#00f2ea]/40 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-xl hover:shadow-[0_10px_40px_-15px_rgba(0,242,234,0.3)]">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#00f2ea]/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 rounded-3xl transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 mb-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#00f2ea]/20 to-transparent flex items-center justify-center text-[#00f2ea] border border-[#00f2ea]/20 group-hover:bg-[#00f2ea]/30 transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8 drop-shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(0,242,234,0.5)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h16a1 1 0 011 1v2.586a1 1 0 01-.293.707l-6.414 6.414a1 1 0 00-.293.707V17l-4 4v-6.586a1 1 0 00-.293-.707L3.293 7.293A1 1 0 013 6.586V4z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] leading-tight">Embudos de Venta (Funnels)</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            Guiamos a los desconocidos hasta que se convierten en compradores.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Tarjeta 3 - Acompañamiento Real -->
                <div class="group relative p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl bg-[#0a0a1a]/50 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-md hover:border-[#39ff14]/40 transition-all duration-500 hover:-translate-y-2 shadow-xl hover:shadow-[0_10px_40px_-15px_rgba(57,255,20,0.3)]">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#39ff14]/10 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 rounded-3xl transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col h-full">
                        <div class="w-16 h-16 mb-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#39ff14]/20 to-transparent flex items-center justify-center text-[#39ff14] border border-[#39ff14]/20 group-hover:bg-[#39ff14]/30 transition-colors">
                            <svg class="w-8 h-8 drop-shadow-[0_0_12px_rgba(57,255,20,0.5)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path></svg>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] leading-tight">Acompañamiento Real</h3>
                        <p class="text-gray-300 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            Transparencia total. Sabrás exactamente qué pasa con cada peso que inviertes.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECCIÓN 4: SERVICIOS DETALLADOS (Cómo lo logramos) -->
    <section class="py-20 relative" style="z-index: 10;">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="text-center mb-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] font-bold mb-6 text-white">¿Cómo lo logramos?</h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                    A través de nuestro portafolio de intervenciones avanzadas diseñadas meticulosamente para potenciar tu marca.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <!-- Servicio A: Publicidad en Meta Ads -->
                <div class="p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl bg-[#0a0a1a]/60 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-md relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-[#1877F2]/40 transition-all duration-300">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 mb-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1877F2]/20 to-transparent flex items-center justify-center text-[#1877F2] border border-[#1877F2]/20 transition-colors">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7 drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(24,119,242,0.5)]" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.469h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.469h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight">Publicidad en Meta Ads <br/><span class="text-lg font-normal text-gray-400 block mt-2">Gestión y optimización de campañas en Facebook e Instagram.</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-[#00f2ea] font-medium mb-6">Llegamos a tu público ideal con anuncios que convierten.</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-4">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#00f2ea] mt-1">✔</span> <span class="text-gray-300">Configuración y estructura de campañas</span></li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#00f2ea] mt-1">✔</span> <span class="text-gray-300">Segmentación avanzada de audiencias</span></li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#00f2ea] mt-1">✔</span> <span class="text-gray-300">Creación de piezas publicitarias persuasivas</span></li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#00f2ea] mt-1">✔</span> <span class="text-gray-300">Pruebas A/B constantes de anuncios</span></li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#00f2ea] mt-1">✔</span> <span class="text-gray-300">Optimización continua de rendimiento</span></li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#00f2ea] mt-1">✔</span> <span class="text-gray-300">Seguimiento detallado de métricas clave (inversión publicitaria independiente).</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Servicio B: Gestión Estratégica -->
                <div class="p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl bg-[#0a0a1a]/60 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-md relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-[#E1306C]/40 transition-all duration-300">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 mb-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#E1306C]/20 to-transparent flex items-center justify-center text-[#E1306C] border border-[#E1306C]/20 transition-colors">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7 drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(225,48,108,0.5)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 18h.01M8 21h8a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H8a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight">Planificación y Ejecución <br/><span class="text-lg font-normal text-gray-400 block mt-2">de contenido digital.</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-[#00f2ea] font-medium mb-6">Construimos una presencia de marca sólida y orientada a resultados.</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-4">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#E1306C] mt-1">✔</span> <span class="text-gray-300">Adaptación de contenido (según plan)</span></li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#E1306C] mt-1">✔</span> <span class="text-gray-300">Uso de plantillas de diseño profesionales</span></li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#E1306C] mt-1">✔</span> <span class="text-gray-300">Calendario mensual de contenidos</span></li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#E1306C] mt-1">✔</span> <span class="text-gray-300">Definición de línea gráfica para potenciar tu identidad visual de manera constante.</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Servicio C: Infraestructura Web -->
                <div class="p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl bg-[#0a0a1a]/60 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-md relative overflow-hidden group hover:border-[#4f46e5]/40 transition-all duration-300">
                    <div class="w-14 h-14 mb-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4f46e5]/20 to-transparent flex items-center justify-center text-[#4f46e5] border border-[#4f46e5]/20 transition-colors">
                        <svg class="w-7 h-7 drop-shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(79,70,229,0.5)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight">Desarrollo Web <br/><span class="text-lg font-normal text-gray-400 block mt-2">Orientado a Conversión.</span></h3>
                    <p class="text-[#00f2ea] font-medium mb-6">Creamos la base técnica para que tus campañas funcionen.</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-4">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#4f46e5] mt-1">✔</span> <span class="text-gray-300">Diseño persuasivo (UX/UI)</span></li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#4f46e5] mt-1">✔</span> <span class="text-gray-300">Velocidad y rendimiento técnico</span></li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-[#4f46e5] mt-1">✔</span> <span class="text-gray-300">100% Adaptables (Mobile-First) e integrados nativamente con herramientas digitales de venta.</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECCIÓN 6: CTA Final -->
    <section class="py-24 relative overflow-hidden" style="z-index: 10; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.8), rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.95));">
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full max-w-lg h-64 bg-[#00f2ea] rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[150px] opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-5xl font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] font-bold mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-tight">
                <span class="text-white">¿Listo para escalar tus ventas?</span> <br class="hidden md:block"/> <span class="text-gradient hover-glow">Hablemos de estrategia.</span>
            </h2>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
                <a href="https://wa.me/56988169404?text=Hola,%20quisiera%20conversar%20sobre%20una%20estrategia%20de%20marketing%20para%20mi%20negocio" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 md:px-14 py-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#25D366] to-[#00f2ea] rounded-full text-[#050511] font-extrabold text-sm md:text-xl tracking-[0.05em] shadow-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(0,242,234,0.3)] transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1 uppercase group">
                    🚀 Agendar mi Asesoría Gratuita
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-3 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</Layout>
